Class RegularReward

java.lang.Object
Interactables.Interactables
Interactables.Reward
Interactables.RegularReward
public class RegularReward extends Reward
RegularReward is a class that represents a regular reward in the game. It extends the Reward class and has methods to create the reward and grant it to a Cyborg.
